#: ../../common/carbonio/usage/files.rst:5
msgid "Carbonio Files provides a file storage system with ability for sharing documents with colleagues, collaborative editing, and document versioning."
msgstr ""

#: ../../common/carbonio/usage/files.rst:9
msgid "Items saved in |file| are shown in the central area and are organised in a folder structure, which initially contain a number of pre-defined shortcut as icons: *Home*, *Shared with me*, *Trash*, *Filters*, and *Uploads*. Files can be arranged in folders under *Home*; a list of recent files and folders accessed by the user is also available, to allow to quickly resume work on these documents."
msgstr ""

#: ../../common/carbonio/usage/files.rst:20
